ient) or havyavaaha (one 
who carries offerings to various gods). That fire=
 can carry various 
auspicious substances to various deities, but does NOT =
like to carry stuff 
like alcohol and meat, even if a deity is willing to r=
eceive the offering. 
If you want to offer alcohol to a deity such as Bhair=
ava, call the deity in 
