arrier 
of impurities) can be used to carry anything, without restrictions.=
 However, 
this fire is not used in homam.

A few deities such as Smashaana=
 Taaraa and Smashaana Kaali may be worshipped 
on a funeral pyre with any m=
aterials. However, such rituals are not 
appropriate for 99.99999999% peopl=
e. Those are only for people who already 
have a very high level of detachm=
ent and a very low level of distinction 
between the polarities of duality,=
 i.e. people who have a very low level of 
mental distinction between thing=
s normally considered highly pure and things 
