worship on funeral pyre, the=
y may get results that are normally considered 
good or results that are no=
rmally considered terrible, but again their 
mental distinction between goo=
d and bad results is very low and they accept 
all results with an equal vi=
sion. Rituals practiced by such aghoris are 
