ip in the fire. In that case, throwing chillies, 
meat and alcohol in fire =
is a strict no-no. Unfortunately, some people do 
not realize it and throw =
these things in their homam fire. This is a 
terrible thing to do.

People =
in this age foolishly mix up principles of duality and non-duality. 
